It was okay, for me.<br>
<br>
I don't think the FF series is all it's declared to be by game zines, sites, and the community of fanboys whose lips seem to have become one with Sakaguchi's exit hole. For my buck, I'd like hours upon hours of adventure, glory, and intrigue, not a full-length movie's worth of dramatic cutscenes interrupted periodically by androgynous heroes talking about their feelings.<br>
